Necromancy
Level: Sor/Wiz 1
Components: V, S
Range: Long
Casting Time: 1 action
Area of Effect: 1 living creature
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes

With this spell the wizard drains the life force from a target and adds it to his own. The target creature suffers 1-4 points of damage, while the wizard gains the same number of hit points. If the wizard goes over his maximum hit point total with this spell, he loses them after 10 rounds.